playstore_details.description:
Phemex is a Singapore based cryptocurrency exchange that specializes in spot and derivatives trading. It is led by 8 former Morgan Stanly Executives with a diverse international team. The exchange allows individuals from all over the world to trade cryptocurrencies through a user-friendly and secure crypto-platform. Phemex stands out as one of the best and most trustworthy exchanges.  

❤️PHEMEX BITCOIN (BTC) & CRYPTO EXCHANGE PLATFORM ADVANTAGES
1. Buy Crypto with Credit and Debit Cards or multiple other payment methods.
2. Derivatives (Perpetual Contract) trading with up to 100x leverage and BTC or USD settlement.
3. Spot markets with ZERO trading fees.
4. Most trusted and reputable crypto exchange in the industry.
5. Beginner and user-friendly interface to buy, sell, or trade digital assets.
6. Simple and fast monitoring of crypto portfolio through website or app.
7. Trade contracts for non-crypto assets such as GOLD.

🥇PHEMEX EXCHANGE & PLATFORM FEATURES
- High Performance
300k transactions per second (TPS), with order response times of less than 1 millisecond.
- Advanced Functionalities
FIX API for institutional traders and Sub-Accounts for quantitative traders.
- Strongest Wallet Security
Cold wallet storage. Transfers require 2-level human scrutiny with offline signatures.
- Access and Support
24 x 7 live multilingual support and. Our CEO is also available on Telegram and Twitter.

🔐PHEMEX SAFETY AND RELIABILITY
Ensuring the safety of every single account is Phemex's top priority.
- Wallet Security
- System Security
- User Account Security
- Trading Engine Security

All assets are 100% stored in cold wallets. Each withdrawal is thoroughly monitored  and requires two-person approval with offline signatures. With the executive team’s advanced Wall Street risk management experience, malicious actions are easily detected and protective measures are quickly deployed.
Learn More Here: https://phemex.com/security

💰PHEMEX SUPPORTED CRYPTOCURRENCIES
✔️Phemex currently offers 13 spot markets: 
BTC USDT, ETH USDT, XRP USDT, LINK USDT, XTZ USDT, LTC USDT, ADA USDT, TRX USDT, ONT USDT, BCH USDT, NEO USDT, DOGE USDT and EOS USDT.

✔️Phemex currently offers 16 perpetual contract markets: 
BTC USD, ETH USD, LINK USD, XTZ USD, LTC USD, GOLD USD, ADA USD, BCH USD, COMP USD, YFI USD, ALGO USD, DOT USD, XRP USD, DOGE USD, AAVE USD and UNI USD.

👉MULTIPLE BONUSES
1.New customers that make a deposit can claim up to 80 USDT in bonus funds.
2.Joining  the Phemex All-Star Affiliate Program allows users to permanently earn up to 50% in commissions on all trading fees collected from the referral network. 

☎️CONTACT US

Email: support@phemex.zendesk.com
Facebook: @Phemex.official
Twitter: @phemex_official
Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/c/Phemex/
Telegram: https://t.me/Phemex_EN
